headline: Global Payments Announces Partnership with Minnesota Twins, Extends Relationship with Dallas Cowboys
summary: ATLANTA, August 05, 2025--Global Payments announces partnership with the Minnesota Twins and extends relationship with the Dallas Cowboys.
